LAMMPS (3 Mar 2020)
# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       H_1.lmp
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (14.19 14.19 14.19)
  2 by 2 by 2 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  65 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.00305993 secs

timestep 0.25

# ---------- Define Interatomic Potential ---------------------
pair_style      reax/c NULL checkqeq no
pair_coeff      * * ffield.reax C H
WARNING: Changed valency_val to valency_boc for X (../reaxc_ffield.cpp:315)
fix             2 all qeq/reax 1 0.0 10.0 1.0e-6 reax/c

#------------ Equilibration of the system -------------------------
